**Starvation: The Unyielding Erosion of Life**

"Starving" redirects here. For the Hailee Steinfeld song, see [Starving (song)](/Starving_(song)).

This article is about extreme malnutrition. For other uses, see [Starvation (disambiguation)](/Starvation_(disambiguation)).

